<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA7">
<l>kaḻaṟoḻutum vāneñcē kārkkaṭaṉīr vēlaip</l>
<l>poḻilaḷanta puḷḷūrtic celva – ṉeḻilaḷantaṅ</l>
<l>keṇṇaṟ kariyāṉai yepporuṭkuñ cēyāṉai</l>
<l>naṇṇaṟ kariyāṉai nām</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We will worship the ankleted [feet] – come, heart, to him who is difficult to fathom,</l>
<l>thus measuring the beauty of the lord with the bird vehicle who measured</l>
<l>the garden  [surrounded] by the water waves of the cloud[-coloured] sea,</l>
<l>him who is far from any matter, him who is difficult to approach for us.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
